data.description: Discover the epitome of country living in this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom brick home on a sprawling 10-acre estate complete with pond, in Hamshire-Fannett ISD! A long, welcoming driveway leads you to this picturesque property, shaded by majestic mature trees that provide a serene and tranquil setting. This property offers an array of desirable features, including a 2-car carport, an outdoor entertainment area, 4-horse stall barn, and a 20x20 shed for all your storage needs. Inside, you'll find an open living area seamlessly integrated with the kitchen, boasting vaulted ceilings and a cozy brick wood-burning fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for gatherings and relaxation. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a spacious walk-in closet, a jetted soaker tub, a sizable tile shower with a rain shower head, and a convenient double vanity. This property is a gem, combining the best of rural living with modern comfort and convenience. Don't miss this one - call us today!
